name: C2G 2m DVI-D Dual Link Digital Video Cable - DVI Cable - 6ft - DVI cable - DVI-D (M) to DVI-D (M) - 6.6 ft - black | Dell USA
description: This precision-engineered cable is ideal for connecting a computer with a DVI-D output to a display or projector with a DVI-D input in corporate and/or medical applications. It is fully compliant with the DVI standard defined by DDWG (Digital Display Working Group) and the DVI-D dual link configuration provides enough bandwidth for resolutions up to 2560x1600 pixels and allows high speed digital video transmission up to 9.9 Gbps. 28 AWG copper conductors are individually insulated in foam-polypropylene to minimize crosstalk, and ensure high speed, error-free transmission.Tri-shielded undermold with dual foil shield and braid shield protects against unwanted EMI/RFI
